reviewText:
DVD came today wrapping looks to be bootlegged - does not work on 2 DVD's
Both same error wrong region code
The grandchildren like the video and the price was right
We could not play this DVD so we had to return for a refund.
My son loves Icarly. I had to purchase a DVD player that plays PAL DVDs, which I wanted anyways. My kid is very happy, which makes me happy.  Many thanks ,,,TOM
